  "title": "Effect of salinity on the seed size and germinability of chickpea and protein content",
  "abstract": "The av. seed protein content in 19 chickpea cv. grown on saline and normal soil was 12 and 21.4%, resp.; 100-seed wt. was 13.7 and 22.2 g, resp. Most of the cv. showed poor germination in saline soil.",
